    description: 'We ingest your knowledge base‚Äîdocuments, FAQs, product info, processes, and brand guidelines. Everything your assistant needs to know.'
  },
  {
    step: '02',
    title: 'Training',
    description: 'The AI learns your business, tone, and edge cases. We fine-tune responses until it sounds like your best employee.'
  },
  {
    step: '03',
    title: 'Deployment',
    description: 'Launch across your chosen channels with monitoring dashboards. Go live with confidence and full visibility.'
  },
  {
    step: '04',
    title: 'Optimization',
    description: 'Continuous learning from real interactions. The assistant gets smarter every day, handling more with higher accuracy.'
  }
